# Color Test - Testing the new styled output!

say "Welcome to StoryScript with colors! 🎨"
say "The text is now styled and beautiful!"

ask "What's your favorite color?" into fav_color

say "Nice choice! " + fav_color + " is a great color!"

choice "Try red" or "Try blue" or "Try green"

if answer is "Try red" then
    say "Red is bold and energetic! ❤️"
end

if answer is "Try blue" then
    say "Blue is calm and peaceful! 💙"
end

if answer is "Try green" then
    say "Green is fresh and natural! 💚"
end

say "Thanks for testing the colorful output!"
